		<RichText x="57" y="661" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="32" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="252" height="36" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="32" color="#ffffff">Wt/Ed: 100/150</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#99ffe5" distance="10" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="56" y="453" fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="270" height="30" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffffff">Large Anemo Slime</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#99ffe5" distance="10" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="255" width="407" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">离得很近时，大型风史莱姆突然鼓起，造成<span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="479" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">离得较远时，大型风史莱姆鼓起，朝玩家冲来，造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">大型风史莱姆起飞并鼓起，朝玩家发射至多4枚的无色气弹，每个造成<span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#10dead">强攻强化：<br/></span><span>连续发射更多的气弹。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="959" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">大型风史莱姆若处在膨胀状态，受到除免疫外的攻击则会立即爆炸死亡；死亡时推开玩家，原地留下短暂的风场。<br/>坠落时，会张开小翅膀缓降不受伤。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
